1772470726260318	botbox-dev	itc:v3:AWLJPJJM5nmSc0AAAAAAQdXqrdvauwAAAAEw8gc		item.create	bn-wtf3	{"description":"Add optional --message flag to 'botbox protocol merge' (consistent with maw ws merge --message). When provided, use it as the commit message in the generated maw ws merge step instead of the auto-detected 'feat: work from <id>' fallback. Also fix the conflict recovery retry step in add_conflict_recovery_guidance which still shows maw ws merge --destroy without --message. Update dev-loop prompt section 7 to show --message in the botbox protocol merge call.","kind":"task","title":"Add --message flag to botbox protocol merge"}	blake3:E-ahU1uKB13r9RdfH1abhxzkkv5X1--5OnHYaYhVx2g
